{
  "texts": [
    "The score range of BLEU is from 0 to 1.",
    "The greater the BLEU score, the better the system's performance is considered to be compared to the references.",
    "The formula for calculating BLEU can be seen in Eq.",
    "(8).BLEU=BP⋅exp (∑ w n log p n N n=1)(8)𝐵𝑃 represents the brevity penalty, adjusting the score to penalize translations shorter than the reference.",
    "𝑁 denotes the maximum number of considered n-grams."
  ]
}